name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForAtheroscleroticCardiovascularDisease
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to atherosclerotic cardiovascular disease (ASCVD) and is listed as a cardiovascular disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes acute coronary syndromes, myocardial infarction, angina, coronary artery disease, stroke, transient ischemic attack, and peripheral arterial disease.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes coronary or other arterial revascularization procedures (e.g., vascular bypass or angioplasty).)
